      "line": 9
    },
    {
      "text": "This is the screw that holds the hinge plate in place.",
      "family": "semantic-thinness",
      "bucket": "no-hits",
      "source": "cases/semantic-thinness/no-hits.md",
      "line": 11
    },
    {
      "text": "The yard felt cold because the sun dropped behind the wall.",
      "family": "semantic-thinness",
      "bucket": "no-hits",
      "source": "cases/semantic-thinness/no-hits.md",
      "line": 13
    },
    {
      "text": "The weight hung from the ceiling bracket.",
