      "bucket": "no-hits",
      "source": "cases/semantic-thinness/no-hits.md",
      "line": 35
    },
    {
      "text": "The room was quiet enough to hear the loose hinge scrape.",
      "family": "semantic-thinness",
      "bucket": "no-hits",
      "source": "cases/semantic-thinness/no-hits.md",
      "line": 37
    },
    {
      "text": "The market shifted three stalls west after the fire.",
